# Instance-tier coordination state — untracked-by-design.
# Preserved on disk, not carried in git. The durable decision-provenance
# surfaces (conversations/, escalations/, sidebars/) and the READMEs stay
# tracked. See ../README.md for the tier boundary; the portable backing is
# Oak PDR-094 / ADR-199 (cross-host — not yet hydrated into castr's estate).
_tmp-*
*.seen
comms/*
comms-seen/*
comms-draft/*
handoffs/*
!handoffs/README.md
active-claims.json
closed-claims.archive.json
shared-comms-log.md
comms-archive/*
!comms-archive/.gitkeep
